00:51:43,740 --> 00:51:45,060
 Kako si vjeran.

618
00:51:45,060 --> 00:51:46,020
 Ne smijemo odbiti.

619
00:51:46,020 --> 00:51:47,480
 I sam si javno još priznao.

620
00:51:47,480 --> 00:51:48,120
 Da, da.

