 Ne, ne, materijalno me ne zanima.

631
00:52:17,920 --> 00:52:20,080
 E, to, to, to, kao, novaci, to...

632
00:52:20,080 --> 00:52:21,420
 Ne, to, ne, to me ne zanima.

